      "content": "i don't want to fight though. i'm just so tired of the struggle. honestly, it feels less like being \"brave\" and more like just being trapped in a cycle of inevitable suffering. if everything is truly doomed, isn't there a kind of peace in just accepting it and letting go? like, instead of fighting a losing battle, why shouldn't people just decide they've had enough and find their own way out of the chaos?",
